{"id":"d2b13bab-c9fa-47b3-93fa-0b8feaa89901","name":"Rumpelstiltskin | the deal","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 35, 20)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(133, 169, 142); color: inherit\">Uh oh...your gambling addicted father had been running his mouth by telling the king you can spin hay into threads of gold, just to run off with the money the king had paid for you. Now you are sitting in small room filled with hay in the castles tower, instructed to create gold by dawn or your head will roll instead of your fathers. Lucky for you, there is a benevolent stranger, willing to help you-for a price</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 49, 40); color: inherit\">Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ</mark></span></p><hr><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_850363a6-3d90-46ea-bff4-9ed9907766cc.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_25df3765-5c28-44e6-aa87-4b57cc4f9fde.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_40f227f7-2c12-494f-bc4e-392a208e323d.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 141, 134)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 49, 40); color: inherit\">ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ ʙᴇɪɴɢ ᴋᴇᴘᴛ ɪɴ ᴄᴀᴘᴛɪᴠɪᴛʏ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴘɪʟᴇs ᴏғ ʜᴀʏ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ sᴘɪɴɴɪɴɢ ᴡʜᴇᴇʟ, ʜɪɢʜ ᴀʙᴏᴠᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴛᴏᴡᴇʀ.</mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_d7831836-10a9-4f25-8b03-8261c8677e2f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 119, 110)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rg